  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd \u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8 \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Jaffna Rani train service started",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna special train service between Jaffna and Kilinochchi started today Monday.",
        "The Railway Department has provided this service for the convenience of government employees and the lecturers and staff of the University of Science and Technology Jaffna.",
        "According to this, Jaffna Queen's train departs from Kangesanthurai at 06.00 am and reaches Murikandi at 8.11 am.",
        "From there again, the train departs for Jaffna at 10.00 am and reaches Jaffna at 11.20 am.",
        "Again the train departs from Kangesanthurai at 02.00 PM and reaches Murikandi at 4.10 PM.",
        "This train will again depart from Murikandi at 4.40 pm and reach Kangesanthurai at 7.20 pm.",
        "One-way fare from Jaffna to Kilinochchi is Rs 90, Jaffna to Palai is Rs 60 and Jaffna to Kodigam is Rs 35."
      ],
